description: Experience the pinnacle of modern city living in this thoughtfully designed 2-bedroom, 2-bath condo located in one of South Boston’s most coveted neighborhoods. Just one block from the vibrant East First Street corridor and within walking distance to the Seaport, East and West Broadway, and Castle Island, this home offers the perfect blend of convenience and lifestyle. Step inside to find a stunning chef’s kitchen featuring custom cabinetry, quartz countertops, a professional-grade JennAir appliance package, and a direct-vented hood — ideal for the culinary enthusiast. The open layout showcases soaring ceilings, oversized windows that flood the space with natural light, and wide-plank hardwood floors throughout. Both bathrooms evoke a spa-like atmosphere, and integrated smart home technology allows you to control your environment with ease. Enjoy the outdoors on your private deck or take advantage of the elevator-accessible, heated garage and impeccably finished common areas.
